Termux is a self-contained Linux environment. Its programs are (for all intents and purposes) exactly the same as their Linux counterparts. This conveys some advantages over the ported applications
Vorteile
Consistency
Termux apps are the same as the Linux versions, from keyboard shortcuts to how you install them.
Kompakt - Schlanke App da kein Android Zusatz-Code
updates - Unabhängigkeit von App Entwicklern

